{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"异象 思恩","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEKv9h9FvOSEwzdVPibeAgy4Dp9OobuK0amF5d0ubuJG37cj20B24NfNl5q1TGC9J8EVBse43ta8zPw/0","content":"我的朋友圈就是一个“小广告贴满的电线杆”和“个人美好生活的黑板报”<div><br></div><div>常规：</div><div>按人群分：</div><div>妈妈们：晒娃是永远的主题、育儿类文章；微商：广告是永远的主题：女性用品居多、课程推广；学生:恶搞，搞笑；其他：吃喝玩乐，最近的热点有车展、网红冰激凌。</div><div>近期热点：人民的名义、无（都是分散的）</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8874,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492750055000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Yuly","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6YKhicCzFyyb5ibeAwJJ3mHXbP6ia1YEZoRjiaoFUFvO8VTzSUN6eKSVxFPrQC3IicSPxXdMFDRE99WrX1uOHNL5n3f3/0","content":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">人民的名义给我们的启示主要是：贪官下场很惨、<a name=\"OLE_LINK4\"></a><a name=\"OLE_LINK3\">贪再多也是空</a>、<a name=\"OLE_LINK6\"></a><a name=\"OLE_LINK5\">不要过于看重仕途</a>、<a name=\"OLE_LINK10\"></a><a name=\"OLE_LINK9\">选对一把手极其重要</a>、真心为群众才能得到群众拥护、反腐道路很艰难！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\n宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 19.2pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">第一，贪官下场很惨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">京州市副市长丁义珍案发后，在神秘人的协助下，乘美航客机潜逃美国洛杉矶。尽管侥幸逃脱追扑，但是到了美国之后，第一天晚上就为今后怎么过辗转反侧、夜不能寐。当接待人员安排他扫地的活儿时，他不愿接受，但对方冷冷地提醒他“你已经不是副市长了”，甚至找人威胁他，他出逃前在宴会上的风光场景，转眼就换成了听人摆布的可怜相，连起码的尊严都没有了，自认为“自由了”的贪官已经完全被恐惧与失落所笼罩。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">第二，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">贪再多也是空</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:black\">国家某部委的项目处长赵德汉被搜查时，衣着朴素，从容地吃着炸酱面，搜查家里和办公室都一无所获，他还自曝每月仅给老母亲寄去</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;color:black\">300</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\ncolor:black\">元钱。看起来如此“清贫”的处长，当被带到藏钱的别墅后，就彻底露馅了。</span>受贿了两亿多的项目处长，到头来什么都没有了，只能到大牢里独自悔恨，但悔之晚矣。<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;color:black\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:black\">第三，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">不要过于看重仕途</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">省公安厅厅长祈同伟一心想当副省长，脑子里只有这一个想法，其他一切都在为此服务。为此，他在工作上瞻前顾后，躲躲闪闪，不敢坚持原则、动真碰硬，尤其怕得罪兼任省委常委的京州市委书记李达康，因为李达康在省委动干部时有发言权，而且还有“沙李配”的传说，为了自己快要透亮的前途，他立场不坚定，工作硬不起来。同时，为了变相靠近和讨好新上任的省委书记，这个公安厅厅长竟然一反常态，主动去与省委书记关系密切的陈岩石家干杂活，真是绞尽脑汁，让人瞧不起。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">第四，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">选对一把手极其重要</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">京州市官场乌烟瘴气，与省委前书记赵立春有直接关系。一方面，从剧中可知，赵立春本人办事不公，有许多负面的评价。另一方面，他选人用人不当、管党治党不力。上梁不正下梁歪，官场风气不正，作为省委书记，难辞其咎。而空降的新省委书记则一身正气，头脑清醒，坚持走群众路线，对贪腐行为零容忍。在与新来的反贪局长侯亮平谈话时，他交了底，无论涉及到谁，都要坚决查处，上不封顶，下不保底。相信，有这样的“一把手”，必能力挽狂澜，重建风清气正的政治生态。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">第五，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">真心为群众才能得到群众拥护</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">陈岩石是从省检察院常务副检察长职务上退休，扛过炸药包，经过枪林弹雨的洗礼，是的的道道的老革命。他一直没忘记党的优秀传统和作风，始终站在人民的立场上，与群众打成一片，尽心竭力为群众办事，被称为“第二检察院”，在群众中威信极高，在解决大风厂的拆迁和安置等问题上，市委市政府不得不多次找陈岩石帮做工作。大风厂工会主席郑西坡胸怀坦荡，真心为职工着想，成了大家的主心骨。群众的眼睛是雪亮的，只要真心为群众着想、帮群众办事，就一定能赢得群众的信任和拥护。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">第六，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">、反腐道路很艰难！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">贪官一般都不甘心束手就擒。他们会利用手中还掌握着的权力，干扰甚至阻挠办案。在准备逮捕丁义珍时，就是因为有人告密和协助，才使其成功潜逃。省反贪局局长陈海因掌握办案的重要线索，而遭致离奇车祸。省检察院派人去省公安厅提举报人蔡成功，遭到市公安局的围堵，对峙局面紧张，剑拔弩张。这些都说明，反腐工作不是一帆风顺的，无论打虎拍蝇，都要付出巨大的代价。在此，向不顾个人安危、坚持原则办案的干部们致敬！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><br>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8392,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492661701000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":true},"code":200}
